Thick cut of beef steak
Beef Bouillon(s)
1 Stick of Butter

Mix cube with a bit of butter until a paste is formed. Rub paste into the meat and let stand for 60 minutes. To a very hot skillet, add meat and tilt pan so to create a well for the butter. With a large spoon, laddle hot butter over steak constantly until desired readiness. Let sit for 10 minutes before serving.

